
**a saiva sect which denies the anavamala to the souls and declares that the souls attain their original pure state when they have gone through the round of births and got themselves rid of all karma**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   ஐக்கவாதசைவம்
-


**a saiva sect which does not recognise the existence of anavamala and holds that siva entrusts the perfected soul with his function**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   பாசுபதம்
-

